resolution: Extracted shared CLI parser/cast modules and consolidated default status-workflow + update.ts mutate field-table. Parts 1-6 all done with zero behavior change; full coverage gate (100% all metrics) and all command/integration specs pass.
expected_result: Shared CLI parser blocks and item-record primitives reduce duplication without changing command behavior.
actual_result: Parser/helper extraction is present in the branch and focused plus full release gates passed.
