  "2026-05-24T21:05:25.783Z",cli-core-dedup-agent,"Parts 1-5 done (zero behavior change). New shared modules: src/cli/commands/legacy-none-tokens.ts (isLegacyNoneToken/assertNoLegacyNoneToken/assertNoLegacyNoneTokens), src/cli/commands/linked-test-parsers.ts (9 parsers + LINKED_TEST_* consts; reconciled create vs test empty-guard via plain falsy check since test pre-trims its args), src/cli/commands/recurrence-parsers.ts (parseEventBoolean/parseDelimitedList/ensureEnumValue/parseRecurrenceRule; reconciled create's intervalRaw!==undefined vs update's truthy guard via emptyNumericGuard 'defined'|'truthy' param). Part 4: added asRecordOrNull (main.ts), asRecordLoose (loader.ts, no array guard), asRecordClone (mcp/server.ts, clones+returns {}) to src/core/shared/primitives.ts -- kept 3 distinct functions because the 3 originals had genuinely different semantics. Part 5: moved DEFAULT_STATUS_DEFINITIONS/DEFAULT_WORKFLOW_DEFINITION to constants.ts as single source; runtime-schema.ts re-exports under historical names; SETTINGS_DEFAULTS.schema references them. Added 4 unit specs (primitives, legacy-none-tokens, linked-test-parsers, recurrence-parsers) and the 3 new cmd modules + primitives.ts to vitest include. pnpm build green; create/update/test/calendar/extension-loader/mcp/settings/runtime-schema specs all pass. Starting Part 6 (update.ts mutate field-table) next."
  "2026-05-24T21:26:12.923Z",cli-core-dedup-agent,"FINAL STATUS - all 6 sub-parts DONE (zero behavior change).\n\nPart 1 (legacy-none) DONE: new src/cli/commands/legacy-none-tokens.ts (isLegacyNoneToken/assertNoLegacyNoneToken/assertNoLegacyNoneTokens + LEGACY_NONE_TOKENS). Removed byte-identical copies from create.ts+update.ts. ~52 LOC dup removed.\n\nPart 2 (linked-test parsers) DONE: new src/cli/commands/linked-test-parsers.ts (9 parsers + LINKED_TEST_ENV_NAME_PATTERN/PROTECTED_ENV_KEYS/PM_CONTEXT_MODE_VALUES + LinkedTestPmContextMode type). create.ts and test.ts now import; test.ts aliases the renamed *Value fns + PM_CONTEXT_MODE_VALUES. Reconciled the create-vs-test empty guard: shared uses plain falsy ; create passes untrimmed raw (preserved), test pre-trims so '' is caught identically. ~190 LOC dup removed.\n\nPart 3 (recurrence/event) DONE: new src/cli/commands/recurrence-parsers.ts (parseEventBoolean/parseDelimitedList/ensureEnumValue/parseRecurrenceRule). update imports ensureEnumValue as ensureEnum. Reconciled create's intervalRaw!==undefined vs update's truthy guard via emptyNumericGuard 'defined'|'truthy' param (create passes 'defined', update 'truthy'). Verified via dist smoke test: create recur_interval= throws, update recur_interval= skips. Removed now-unused RECURRENCE_* / weekdayOrderIndex / RecurrenceRule imports from both. ~150 LOC dup removed.\n\nPart 4 (asRecord) DONE: added asRecordOrNull (main.ts semantics: null for non-obj/null/array, no clone), asRecordLoose (loader.ts: no array guard), asRecordClone (mcp/server.ts: clones, returns {}) to src/core/shared/primitives.ts. Kept 3 distinct functions because the 3 originals had GENUINELY DIFFERENT behavior - a single fn would have changed behavior. All 3 call sites updated.\n\nPart 5 (default status/workflow) DONE: moved canonical DEFAULT_STATUS_DEFINITIONS + DEFAULT_WORKFLOW_DEFINITION to src/core/shared/constants.ts (single source). runtime-schema.ts re-exports them as DEFAULT_RUNTIME_STATUS_DEFINITIONS/DEFAULT_RUNTIME_WORKFLOW; SETTINGS_DEFAULTS.schema references them via spread. No import cycle.\n\nPart 6 (update.ts mutate field-table) DONE (not reverted): added setOrClearScalar + setOrClearTrimScalar helpers inside mutate() and replaced 30 near-identical scalar blocks IN PLACE (preserving exact changedFields push order) - 20 trim scalars, acceptance_criteria (raw, no trim), deadline/estimated_minutes/risk/confidence/severity/regression (transform variants). Left command-specific blocks untouched: assignee (empty throw), parent (resolvedParentValue), sprint/release (warnings), order (int validation), blocked_by (dep edge side-effect), collections, runtime/extension fields. update.ts net -296 LOC.\n\nNew unit specs (100% cover the new included modules): tests/unit/shared-primitives.spec.ts, legacy-none-tokens.spec.ts, linked-test-parsers.spec.ts, recurrence-parsers.spec.ts. vitest.config.ts include += primitives.ts + 3 new cmd modules. Removed primitives.ts from the release-readiness-runtime uncovered-list guard. 3 provably-dead defensive branches in linked-test-parsers.ts marked /* c8 ignore */.\n\nNet: ~787 LOC removed from create/update/test; 394 LOC of single-source shared modules added.\n\nTests run + results (all PASS):\n- node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- create-command/update-command/test-command/calendar-command/extension-loader/settings-store/settings-validator/runtime-schema-command-flags/update-many-command/deps-command + 4 new module specs + release-readiness-runtime + mcp-dynamic-package-actions/claude-plugin-contract => all green\n- node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage => 1708 tests pass, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines (gate green)\n- pnpm build + pnpm typecheck => green\n- dist smoke tests: trim/transform/unset/legacy-none-normalize/recurrence-guard/linked-test all behave identically."
close_reason: "Completed all 6 dedup sub-parts with zero behavior change; build, typecheck, and 100% coverage gate green."
